{"title":"ERROR 1045 (28000)_ Access denied for user ‘root‘@‘localhost‘ (using password_ YES)","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.057Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/ERROR 1045 (28000)_ Access denied for user ‘root‘@‘localhost‘ (using password_ YES)","updated":"2023-07-28T09:15:28.368Z","content":"<p>mysql8.0以上版本登陆出现<br>\nRROR 1045 (28000): Access denied for user ‘root’@‘localhost’ (using password: YES)</p>\n<p>我是因为设置了root@%的密码，但root@localhost的密码和root@%密码不一致，所以输入root@%的密码登陆不上去。<br>\n1、如果你此时无法登陆mysql，可以设置mysql无密码登陆。如果能登陆，直接看第2步</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#修改mysql配置文件，在[mysqld]下面加上 skip-grant-tables</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/mysql/my.cnf</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#然后重启mysql，再无密码登陆</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">service mysql restart</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql -uroot -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、此时问题转换为修改root@localhost的密码。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">use mysql;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看端口、用户、密码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> host, user, authentication_string, plugin from user;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ba87710ccf934a7ca35e9b2911627f8a.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>可以看到我这个localhost端口上的root账户密码和远程%端口上的root账户是密码是不一样的。<br>\n此时我们修改他们的密码一致即可；</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#修改localhost的密码，最好和远程%端口的密码一致，方便记忆</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">alter user <span class=\"string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class=\"string\">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span> identified with mysql_native_password by <span class=\"string\">&#x27;$&#123;新密码&#125;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#刷新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">flush privileges;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时密码已经更新。<br>\n3、如果刚刚你修改了<code>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</code>，再将里面的<code>skip-grant-tables</code>去掉。如果没有做第1步，则忽略此项操作。</p>\n<p>同理，如果你远程</p>\n","next":{"title":"ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements","link":"2023/07/28/ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/ERROR 1045 (28000)_ Access denied for user ‘root‘@‘localhost‘ (using password_ YES)/","reading_time":"329 字约 2 分钟"}